::Zardus::

Zardus looks over at Battera as she lands (he was outside).

"I'm right here," he says, stepping out of the shadows of the exit. His 
completely black body had hidden him from view, his red optics now looking at 
Battera with curiousity, "What did Feline want to tell me?"
